scopes.name: schedule_only
scopes.explanation: Lines 325-477 contain the full text of the Schedule to the ISDA Master Agreement, starting with the heading 'SCHEDULE' and including all the negotiated terms, elections, and party-specific provisions. The lines before this are the standard pre-printed Master Agreement, and the lines after this (from 478 onward) are appendices and the Credit Support Annex, which are not part of the Schedule itself.
